    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving mill utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels via an M-variable limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring the McPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry provides exceptional turn-in and lateral grip. A mechanically sound example ready for the twisties.",
