      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2019 executive sedan is the ideal choice for a buyer seeking a blend of luxury and proven reliability. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Charcoal Metallic that retains a high gloss, showing only minor stone chips on the hood and a small, faint scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of premium black leather and brushed aluminum accents; the seats are in excellent shape with no rips or stains, showing only light softening of the leather on the driver's side. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium 12-speaker sound system and navigation, is in perfect working order. Mechanically, this car has been fastidiously maintained with records to prove it. The engine idles quietly and pulls strongly through all gears, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. It sits on a set of high-performance all-season tires with plenty of life left. This is a solid, honest vehicle that has many miles of comfortable driving ahead.",
